    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="码云SSH设置-使用码云"><a href="#码云SSH设置-使用码云" class="headerlink" title="码云SSH设置 使用码云"></a>码云SSH设置 <a href="https://www.liaoxuefeng.com/wiki/0013739516305929606dd18361248578c67b8067c8c017b000/00150154460073692d151e784de4d718c67ce836f72c7c4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">使用码云</a></h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"714074509@qq.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ 三个回车，保存到 <span class="built_in">cd</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub  放到github和gitee的ssh中</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@gitee.com</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@github.com</span><br><span class="line">$ 有本地库</span><br><span class="line">$ git remote add github git@github.com:niujianyin/test.git //关联github远程库</span><br><span class="line">$ git remote -v // 查看远程信息</span><br><span class="line">$ git push origin master -f // 强行让本地分支覆盖远程分支</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br><span class="line">$ 以下是使用自定义gitee_rsa,默认是id_rsa</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">"niujianyin@gitee.com"</span></span><br><span class="line">$ gitee_rsa</span><br><span class="line">$ 空格（不输入密码）</span><br><span class="line">$ https://gitee.com/profile/sshkeys  把~/.ssh/gitee_rsa.pub公钥内容复制并粘贴</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh-add ~/.ssh/gitee_rsa //添加本地私钥 Identity added;sshkey放进系统</span><br><span class="line">$ ssh -T git@gitee.com  // Welcome to Gitee.com, niujianyin!</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>cd ~/.ssh/<br>id_rsa.pub <a href="mailto:714074509@qq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">714074509@qq.com</a>  放了github的ssh<br>gitee_rsa.pub <a href="mailto:niujianyin@gitee.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niujianyin@gitee.com</a>  放了gitee的ssh</p>]]></content>
    
