    <title>ThinkPHP 5.0开发微信小程序商场打通全栈项目架构</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/03/15/ThinkPHP-5-0%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E5%95%86%E5%9C%BA%E6%89%93%E9%80%9A%E5%85%A8%E6%A0%88%E9%A1%B9%E7%9B%AE%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/03/15/ThinkPHP-5-0开发微信小程序商场打通全栈项目架构/</id>
    <published>2018-03-15T03:27:12.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-03-16T01:47:34.039Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>所有安装都在mac环境下。</p><h3 id="环境和工具-XAMPP（Apache-MySQL-PHP-PERL）是一个功能强大的建站集成软件包"><a href="#环境和工具-XAMPP（Apache-MySQL-PHP-PERL）是一个功能强大的建站集成软件包" class="headerlink" title="环境和工具 XAMPP（Apache+MySQL+PHP+PERL）是一个功能强大的建站集成软件包"></a>环境和工具 XAMPP（Apache+MySQL+PHP+PERL）是一个功能强大的建站集成软件包</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ Web框架  ThinkPHP 5.07  （TP5）</span><br><span class="line">$ PHP 7.1.7</span><br><span class="line">$ MySQL</span><br><span class="line">$ Apache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="开发工具"><a href="#开发工具" class="headerlink" title="开发工具"></a>开发工具</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ PHPStorm</span><br><span class="line">$ 微信开发者工具</span><br><span class="line">$ PostMan  / eolinker / Fiddler / Charles</span><br><span class="line">$ Navicat //强大的数据库管理和设计工具</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="XAMPP-安装（官网或者百度软件中心搜索）-权限问题，确保下载文件夹有访问权限，chmod-777-R-或者-sudo"><a href="#XAMPP-安装（官网或者百度软件中心搜索）-权限问题，确保下载文件夹有访问权限，chmod-777-R-或者-sudo" class="headerlink" title="XAMPP 安装（官网或者百度软件中心搜索） 权限问题，确保下载文件夹有访问权限，chmod 777 -R 或者 sudo"></a>XAMPP 安装（官网或者百度软件中心搜索） 权限问题，确保下载文件夹有访问权限，chmod 777 -R 或者 sudo</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ 安装完成后  http://localhost:80 到XAMPP默认页面，安装成功;XAMPP Apache是内置的，有可能会和mac自带Apache冲突</span><br><span class="line">$ 下面命令是操作mac自带apache的，端口占用，请sudo /usr/sbin/apachectl stop</span><br><span class="line">$ 重启apache：sudo /usr/sbin/apachectl restart</span><br><span class="line">$ 关闭apache：sudo /usr/sbin/apachectl stop</span><br><span class="line">$ 开启apache：sudo /usr/sbin/apachectl start</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ 测试mysql 安装成功  (sudo /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/mysql.server start)</span><br><span class="line">$ cd  /Applications/xampp/bin</span><br><span class="line">$ ./mysql -u root -p  (ln -s /applications/xampp/bin/mysql /usr/bin)</span><br><span class="line">$ show databases;</span><br><span class="line">$ exit  </span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ 安装TP5 (下载ThinkPHP 5即可) </span><br><span class="line">$ ThinkPHP5.0完全开发手册 </span><br><span class="line">$ https://www.kancloud.cn/manual/thinkphp5/118006  </span><br><span class="line">$ Git安装 tag v5.0.7  应用项目think (think-5.0.7 改名为 zerg)   核心框架 framework (framework-5.0.7 改名为 thinkphp,放到zerg文件夹内)</span><br><span class="line">$ /Applications/xampp/htdocs  // XAMPP Web根目录 所有Web应用（zerg文件夹）都放这里 </span><br><span class="line">$ http://localhost/zerg/public  //显示ThinkPHP V5 安装成功  默认index.php缺省</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ 服务器程序: Zerg</span><br><span class="line">$ 客户端小程序: Protoss</span><br><span class="line">$ CMS: Terran</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="PHPStorm"><a href="#PHPStorm" class="headerlink" title="PHPStorm"></a>PHPStorm</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ PHPstorm激活码 http://www.0-php.com:1017</span><br><span class="line">$ PHPstorm 打开项目 /Applications/xampp/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg</span><br><span class="line">$ 设置：PHPstorm &gt; Preference...(Command + ,) </span><br><span class="line">$ Appearance &amp; Behavior &gt; Appearance &gt; Theme &gt; Darcula</span><br><span class="line">$ shift + command + o　　搜索项目中的文件</span><br><span class="line">$ command + E 打开最近的文件</span><br><span class="line">$ ctrl+~  瞬间切换主题</span><br><span class="line">$ 设置：PHPstorm &gt; Preference...(Command + ,) &gt; keymap 搜索快捷键，如 Recent Files</span><br><span class="line">$ command + Tab 切换选择文件</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ PHPStorm IDE 快捷键(MAC)</span><br><span class="line">$ ⌘——Command</span><br><span class="line">$ ⌃ ——Control</span><br><span class="line">$ ⌥——Option/Alt</span><br><span class="line">$ ⇧——Shift</span><br><span class="line">$ ⇪——Caps Lock</span><br><span class="line">$ fn——功能键就是fn</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="TP5层次结构"><a href="#TP5层次结构" class="headerlink" title="TP5层次结构"></a>TP5层次结构</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ 入口文件，所有请求都必须经过index.php (zerg/public/index.php) ，可以有多个</span><br><span class="line">$ 可以有多个应用 如(zerg/application)   // 在入口文件定义应用目录 define(&apos;APP_PATH&apos;, __DIR__ . &apos;/../application/&apos;); </span><br><span class="line">$ application（应用）&gt; api (modules模块) &gt; controller (控制) - model(数据模型) - service(业务逻辑) - validate(验证) &gt; Banner.php(具体控制器) &gt; action(操作) &gt; 操作model(数据模型)/service(业务逻辑)</span><br><span class="line">$ vendor 安装第三方类库和插件</span><br><span class="line">$ thinkphp 核心框架 用于支持TP5框架运行</span><br><span class="line">$ runtime 写入运行文件，日志文件和缓存文件</span><br><span class="line">$ public 外部站点目录，对外唯一可以访问</span><br><span class="line">$ extend 第三方类库 （自己的类库）</span><br><span class="line">$ cd /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/public</span><br><span class="line">$ php -S localhost:9000 router.php (TP5 自带服务器，基本不用)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="PHPStorm下断点调试代码"><a href="#PHPStorm下断点调试代码" class="headerlink" title="PHPStorm下断点调试代码"></a>PHPStorm下断点调试代码</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ xdebug 安装</span><br><span class="line">$ http://localhost/dashboard/phpinfo.php</span><br><span class="line">$ https://xdebug.org/wizard.php  把 phpinfo()页面源代码 信息粘贴进去</span><br><span class="line">$ 按照提示操作，不过中间第四步和五部需要使用XAMPP自带的phpize</span><br><span class="line">$ 重点提示（这个坑搞了一天）</span><br><span class="line">// 通过phpize安装xdebug（http://blog.csdn.net/coderDerek/article/details/75208418）</span><br><span class="line">// 这个很坑，phpize编译一定要选取 /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize-7.0.2，也就是要选XAMPP安装包，不要选mac默认php带的phpize（/usr/local/webserver/php/bin/phpize）</span><br><span class="line">$ /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/phpize-7.0.2</span><br><span class="line">$ ./configure -with-php-config=/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/bin/php-config-7.0.2</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ subl /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/php.ini  //修改增加配置如下</span><br><span class="line">$ [xdebug]</span><br><span class="line">$ zend_extension = /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/lib/php/extensions/no-debug-non-zts-20151012/xdebug.so</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_autostart=on</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_enable=on</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_handler=dbgp</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_host=localhost</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_port=9000</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.profiler_enable=1</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.remote_log=&quot;/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/logs/xdebug.log&quot;</span><br><span class="line">$ xdebug.idekey=&quot;PHPSTORM&quot;</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ 重启XAMPP下apache（XAMPP在mac上软件名:manager-osx）</span><br><span class="line">$ 在 http://localhost/dashboard/phpinfo.php 中搜索xdebug 信息存在安装成功；php -m | grep xdebug 网上这个方法不会有显示，原因是php调用的本机,不是XAMPP下的</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ 到PHPStorm中右上角小三角 PHP Web Application  增加调试服务器，Name：zerg，Server:Apache(localhost:80); Start URL (/zerg/public/index.php)  之后不用每次修改，直接在把调试码加到url后即可</span><br><span class="line">$</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="TP5-URL路径格式"><a href="#TP5-URL路径格式" class="headerlink" title="TP5 URL路径格式"></a>TP5 URL路径格式</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ http://serverName/index.php/module/controller/action/[param/value...]</span><br><span class="line">$ http://localhost/zerg/public/index.php/index/index/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>url不区分大小写 index tp5默认保留路径<br>url区分大小写 :config.php   url设置   :url_convert false<br>官方不区分大小写  path_info<br>不会使用  写接口 最好不写兼容模式和path_info<br>缺点：太长，url路径暴露服务器文件结构,不够灵活 不能很好的支持Url语义化,路由解决</p><h3 id="TP5-路由模式-application-config-php-url-route-must-true"><a href="#TP5-路由模式-application-config-php-url-route-must-true" class="headerlink" title="TP5 路由模式  application/config.php url_route_must:true"></a>TP5 路由模式  application/config.php url_route_must:true</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ application &gt; sample &gt; controller &gt; Test.php &gt; hello</span><br><span class="line">$ localhost/zerg/public/sample/test/hello  (controller这个不需要体现，地址中大小写不区分)</span><br><span class="line">$ z.cn/sample/test/hello (配置虚拟主机后地址)</span><br><span class="line">$ z.cn/模块/控制器/方法</span><br><span class="line">$ 新建Test需要有命名空间，PHPstorm &gt; Directories &gt; Sources模式下 &gt; P小三角 &gt; 写app，之后新建文件自动补全</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="XAMPP-下配置虚拟主机"><a href="#XAMPP-下配置虚拟主机" class="headerlink" title="XAMPP 下配置虚拟主机"></a>XAMPP 下配置虚拟主机</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ subl /etc/hosts //配置hosts</span><br><span class="line">$ 127.0.0.1 z.cn （末尾添加）</span><br><span class="line">$ </span><br><span class="line">$ subl /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/httpd.conf </span><br><span class="line">$ Include /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf  // 增加这行</span><br><span class="line">$ #subl /private/etc/apache2/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf //mac自带apache配置文件，这个不修改</span><br><span class="line">$ subl /Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/etc/extra/httpd-vhosts.conf //XAMPP下apache配置文件添加如下代码</span><br><span class="line"># localhost  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">    ServerName localhost  </span><br><span class="line">    DocumentRoot &quot;/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs&quot;  </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Directory &quot;/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs&quot;&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks Includes execCGI  </span><br><span class="line">        AllowOverride All  </span><br><span class="line">        Require all granted  </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/Directory&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;  </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># My custom host  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">    ServerName z.cn</span><br><span class="line">    ServerAlias z.cn</span><br><span class="line">    DocumentRoot &quot;/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/public&quot;  </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Directory &quot;/Applications/XAMPP/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/public&quot;&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">        Options Indexes FollowSymLinks Includes ExecCGI  </span><br><span class="line">        AllowOverride All  </span><br><span class="line">        Require all granted  </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/Directory&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">    ErrorLog &quot;logs/z.cn-error_log&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    CustomLog &quot;logs/z.cn-access_log&quot; common</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="TP5-三种URL访问模式-Applications-xampp-xamppfiles-htdocs-zerg-application-route-php"><a href="#TP5-三种URL访问模式-Applications-xampp-xamppfiles-htdocs-zerg-application-route-php" class="headerlink" title="TP5 三种URL访问模式  /Applications/xampp/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/application/route.php"></a>TP5 三种URL访问模式  /Applications/xampp/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/application/route.php</h3><pre><code>$ 选用动态注册(路由模式)； 配置模式(PATH_INFO) 弃用 $ use think\Route;$ Route::rule(&apos;hello&apos;, &apos;sample/Test/hello&apos;);$ /Applications/xampp/xamppfiles/htdocs/zerg/application/config.php url_route_must: true //强制使用路由模式$ 定义路由$ Route::rule(&apos;路由表达式&apos;，&apos;路由地址&apos;,&apos;请求类型&apos;,&apos;路由参数(参数)&apos;,&apos;变量规则(数组)&apos;)$ Route::rule(&apos;hello&apos;,&apos;sample/Test/hello&apos;,&apos;GET|POST&apos;,[&apos;https&apos;=false]);</code></pre><p>GET POST DELETE  PUT<br>请求类型没有 默认会变成<em> 任意请求类型  任意一种类型都支持<br>路由参数<br>https 检测是否https请求  不是https 不能访问<br>Route::any(); 对应</em></p><p>获取参数的方法：<br>1.传统获取参数，方法中 hello($id,$name)<br>  a.路由中传参 b.?问号方式传参 c.body里传参<br>2.使用tp5 Request类<br>  Request::instance()-&gt;param();获取所有参数。<br>  Request::instance()-&gt;route();获取路径里参数。<br>  Request::instance()-&gt;get();获取?后面参数。<br>  Request::instance()-&gt;post();获取post参数。<br>依赖注入：hello(Request $request)<br>3.使用助手函数：input(‘param.id’)</p><h3 id="Navicat-强大的数据库管理和设计工具"><a href="#Navicat-强大的数据库管理和设计工具" class="headerlink" title="Navicat 强大的数据库管理和设计工具"></a>Navicat 强大的数据库管理和设计工具</h3>]]></content>
    
